Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.19,0:01:00.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}驅散匯集的黑暗繼續前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:16.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつになったら失くした未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:16.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要到什麼時候 失去的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:22.87,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}私ここでまた見ること出来るの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:22.87,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我才能在這裡再次眺望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:27.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}溢れ出した不安の影を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:27.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}無數次撕裂漫溢的不安的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:33.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}何度でも裂いてこの世界歩んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:33.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}在這世界上不斷前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:38.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}止めどなく刻まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:38.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}打上無盡的刻印的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:44.29,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}時は今始まり告げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:44.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}時間此刻宣告著開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:49.39,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}変わらない思いをのせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:49.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}乘載著不變的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:54.87,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}閉ざされた扉開けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:54.87,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去打開閉鎖的門扉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:02:00.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}目覚めたココロは走り出した 未来を描くため
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:02:00.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}甦醒的心為了描繪未來而奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:05.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}難しい道で立ち止まっても空は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:05.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}即使在泥濘的路上停滯不前天空也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:10.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}綺麗な青さでいつも待っててくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:10.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}帶著美麗的蔚藍一直等待著我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}だからこわくない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}所以不必害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:15.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}もう何があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:15.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:17.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)\fad(250,0)\blur2}第2話    我想那還真是令人高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}くじけない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}也不會氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:23.95,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}本字幕由華盟字幕社&澄空學園字幕組製作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓 昨天好像回來很晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:27.09,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}翻譯：リボーン / detectivexsc  校對：mafuyu / 豆奶  後期：yulius / 阿爽 / 9416-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為我被叫去學姊家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}算了 門禁什麼的我就不囉嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是晚飯前要給家裡打個招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}其他人真的是看不見的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好漂亮的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我是一個人住所以不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也沒有準備什麼像樣的東西招待你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美姐 真是太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯 超好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}既然被丘比選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你們也就不是外人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我想需要一定程度的說明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯嗯 隨你問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽 搞反了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}{\pos(340,326)\fs16\b1}soul gem
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這是靈魂寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}被丘比選中的女孩子通過契約而產生的寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}既是魔力的源泉 也是作為魔法少女的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}契約是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我可以實現你們任何一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}啊 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}願望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}什麼願望都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}無論什麼奇跡我都可以引發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哇 金銀財寶或者不老不死什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}滿漢全席什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不 最後的那個稍稍有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是 以此為代價做成的就是靈魂寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}得到這寶石的人會被賦予與魔女戰鬥的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}吶 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}如果 我是說如果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}如果說用魔法可以實現任何的願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}讓兩個職員從我身邊滾蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}社長也是啊 已經不是可以逞強蠻幹的年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}差不多該考慮退休了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}可是卻沒有後繼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}乾脆媽媽來當社長不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}還有這一手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}先跟營業部疏通好關係的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}企劃部和總務也會唯命是從
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那樣的話問題就是那禿子經理了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那傢伙嗎 除掉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}媽媽 眼神好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔女是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}跟魔法少女不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}如果說從願望誕生的是魔法少女的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔女就是通過詛咒誕生的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}像魔法少女傳播希望一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔女則散佈絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}而且因為一般人見不到她們的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}性質更加惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不安和猜疑心 過度的憤怒和憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}將這些災難的種子帶來世間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}無法查明的自殺或殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}有相當的機率就是因為魔女的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}化成沒有實體的惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}從內部開始侵蝕人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}既然有那麼糟糕的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼誰都沒有發覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為魔女一直都潛藏在結界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}絕不會在人前現身的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}剛才你們誤闖入的那個迷宮一樣的地方就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那是相當危險的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}被那個所吞噬的人一般是無法活著回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美姐一直和那麼可怕的東西戰鬥著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是的 拼上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以你們最好也慎重選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}被丘比選中的你們擁有可以實現任何願望的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是那是伴隨著會死的危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}啊 好煩惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}於是我有個提案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你們兩個要不要暫時陪著我消滅魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}和魔女的戰鬥是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就用你們自己的眼睛來確認好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}在此之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我想你們可以好好考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}到底有沒有值得冒險來實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}早上…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}早上好 小爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}啊…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼了 小爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}果然這傢伙只有我們才看得見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不 沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}走吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只在腦袋裡想好像就可以對話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我們已經擁有那種魔法般的能力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不不 現在還只是我在中間做中介而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是說悄悄話很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}總有點奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}兩位剛才開始怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}一直在頻頻相互使眼色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這個是… 這個…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}難道兩位已經是眉目傳情心有靈犀的關係了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}竟然只一天就親近到了這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}昨天在那之後到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不 那怎麼也是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然確實發生了…很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是 這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}兩位同為女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那是禁斷的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}愛的形式啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}書包忘了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}今天的仁美總感覺像小爽似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你那是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你這樣悠哉悠哉地跟到學校來不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我不是說過嗎 昨天的那傢伙是我們班新來的轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你不是被她盯上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我覺得學校反而更安全些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美是三年級生 教室離得有些遠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不必擔心 說的話我都聽得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這種程度的距離 是在心靈感應的有效範圍內的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個… 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我會看好你們的 安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}而且那孩子應該也不會在人前襲擊你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}說曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個轉學生也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個…也是魔法少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}跟麻美姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是呢 應該不會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好像擁有相當強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是 那樣的話應該也是跟魔女戰鬥的正義的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那為什麼還要突然襲擊小圓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}她的目標是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}可能是想阻止新的魔法少女誕生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}既然是和相同的敵人戰鬥的話 同伴不是越多越好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}並不完全是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}反而是競爭的時候比較多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼這樣 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}打倒魔女的話就會得到相應的回報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以根據時機和場合 也會有為了搶功而衝突的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也就是說那傢伙開始就知道丘比會去找小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以早上才會來找麻煩的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}大概就是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不用在意 小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那傢伙來找麻煩的話 我就打飛她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}反正麻美姐也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是啊 美樹同學姑且不論
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}有我在的話是不要緊的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}別說啥姑且不論啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}吶 就像以前學過的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}發起動作的人或物作主語時的表現形式叫做主動態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:11:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}相反所謂的被動態是指B被A做了什麼那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}承受動作的人或物作為主語的表現形式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這種被動態的形式就是be動詞加上過去分詞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}例如「He likes me」 他喜歡我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}吶 小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}願望考慮好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒 小爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我也是完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}還以為要想多少就能想到多少的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然想要的東西想做的事都有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}一關係到性命果然還是會猶豫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}會去想 真的值得那麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}真意外呢 大多數的孩子都是不假思索的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不過肯定是因為我們是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哎 是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是的 幸福的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}其實應該不稀奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不惜拼上性命也想實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}抱著那種想法的人 在世上應該有很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以 找不到那種願望的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就是只知道那種程度的不幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}受到太多的恩惠 變成了笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼會是我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不覺得不公平嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}真正希望得到這種機會的人應該另有他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}繼續昨天的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不 我沒有那種打算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然我想在它跟鹿目圓接觸之前解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}現在也已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那麼 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你也打算成為魔法少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}輪不到你來說三道四的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}昨天的話還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那就好 希望我的忠告不要白費
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個 你是許下什麼願望才成為魔法少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}仁美 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}今天我們稍微有點事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哎呀 是要保密的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}太令人羨慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你們兩人之間已經容不下我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不… 所以說不是那回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}今天放學一起去咖啡店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我今天也有些急事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那麼魔法少女體驗課程第一彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}鼓起幹勁開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然不知道算不算是準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但我把這個帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我想總比什麼都沒有要好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這個…你有這份覺悟那是最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓你帶了什麼來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}總…總之 我覺得要先考慮一下衣著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯 作為熱情來說足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我算服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}真是敗給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這是昨天的魔女留下來的魔力的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}基本上尋找魔女是靠走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}像這樣跟著靈魂寶石所捕捉到的魔女的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}意外地樸素呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}光完全沒有變化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為從被它逃掉已經過了一晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}足跡也變少了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個時候馬上追上去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然也許可以收拾它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但並不是值得放著你們不顧的優先選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯 果然麻美姐是正義的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}與此相反 那個轉學生真是令人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}真的是個壞孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}喂 麻美姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔女可能藏匿的地點就沒有一點頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}受魔女的詛咒影響的大多是交通事故和傷害事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以大馬路和容易發生爭吵的娛樂區得優先調查才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}另外就是適合自殺的無人場所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}還有要是佔據了醫院之類的那就太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}原本就虛弱的人們再被吸去生命力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}結果會慘不忍睹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}非常強大的魔力波動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也許很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒錯 是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美姐 那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔女的唇印
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒關係 只是昏過去了罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}今天不會再讓你逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然是聊勝於無的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不過這應該能起到防身的作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}絕對不要離開我的身邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}別過來 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼樣 兩位害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然害怕 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}加油 馬上就是結界的最深處了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}看 那就是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}要和那個戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒事的 我怎麼會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}退後點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}在未來的學妹面前我可不能太丟臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Tiro Finale
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}{\pos(292,326)\fs16\b1}grief seed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這是悲歎之種 魔女的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}卵…卵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}運氣好的話 有時魔女會隨身帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒關係 這個狀態下是很安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}反而是能起到作用的貴重品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我的靈魂寶石比起昨晚顏色有點渾濁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.58,0:22:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是用悲歎之種的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}變清澈了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這樣一來我消耗的魔力也復原了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}之前說過的消滅魔女的回報也就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}應該還能再用一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美炎同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}還是說和別人分享你覺得不服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這是你的獵物 是只屬於你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是嗎 這就是你的回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}果然是個討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}如果能好好相處就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:22:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}如果相互都是這麼想的話…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}咦？ 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}討厭 我… 為什麼…會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼會做那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒關係 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你只是做了個噩夢罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}事件告一段落…的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}想要實現的願望什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然對我來說太難了 還不能馬上決定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是為了幫助別人而努力的麻美姐的樣子真是非常的棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就算是這樣的我 如果能像那樣幫助誰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那還真是令人高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我不禁這樣想道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:59.22,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}揮揮手道一聲再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:59.22,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}それじゃまたねって 手を振って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.26,0:24:04.01,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}勉強自己微笑 變得寂寞起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.26,0:24:04.01,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}無理に笑って 寂しくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:18.99,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}十字路口的訊號 遙遠的喇叭聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:18.99,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}交差点信号 遠くのクラクション
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:26.05,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}未曾相識的某人 相互歡笑的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:26.05,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}知らない誰かの 笑いあう声
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:33.19,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}今天獨自走在這條熟悉的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:33.19,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}今日は一人で歩く 通い慣れた街
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.31,0:24:38.21,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}但是不知為何總覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.31,0:24:38.21,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}でもいつもよりもなんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.26,0:24:43.93,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}自己比平時顯得稍微渺小了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.26,0:24:43.93,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}自分がちょっと 小さく思えるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.11,0:24:49.19,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}揮揮手道一聲再見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.11,0:24:49.19,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}それじゃまたねって 手を振って
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.19,0:24:53.79,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}努力擠出笑容 變得寂寞起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.19,0:24:53.79,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}笑顔を作って 寂しくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.17,0:25:00.46,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}其實遠遠沒有和你交談足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.17,0:25:00.46,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}ほんとはまだ 話し足りないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.57,0:25:04.54,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}那就以再見這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.57,0:25:04.54,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}それじゃまたねって言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:09.06,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}說出「還能再會」的謊言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.56,0:25:09.06,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}「また会える」って嘘をついて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.51,0:25:15.24,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}用一如往常的笑容說出口哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.51,0:25:15.24,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}いつも通りの 笑顔で言うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.27,0:25:18.49,edcn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}那麼 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.27,0:25:18.49,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5\}また あした
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.07,0:25:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只是在逞強硬裝樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.12,0:25:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就算害怕難過也不能向別人吐露
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.37,0:25:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只能孤單一個人哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.61,0:25:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}魔法少女才不是什麼好差事呢
